cks\"/>\n|-\n| \u2014\n|{{sort|?|MF}}\n!scope=\"row\"| {{flagicon|IND}} [[Bidyananda Singh]]\n| [[Atl\u00e9tico de Kolkata]]\n| N/A\n| 31 July 2017\n|<ref name=\"Bidyananda and Robinson\"/>\n|-\n| 38\n|{{sort|38|MF}}\n!scope=\"row\"| {{flagicon|IND}} [[Robinson Singh]]\n| [[Mohun Bagan A.C.|Mohun Bagan]]\n| N/A\n| 31 July 2017\n|<ref name=\"Bidyananda and Robinson\"/>\n|-\n| 9\n|{{sort|9|FW}}\n!scope=\"row\"| {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Braulio N\u00f3brega]]\n|{{flagicon|CYP}} [[Doxa Katokopias FC|Doxa]]\n| Free agent\n| 7 August 2017\n|<ref name=\"Braulio\"/>\n|-\n| 39\n|{{sort|39|FW}}\n!scope=\"row\"| {{flagicon|IND}} Leon Augustine\n|[[Bengaluru FC Academy]]\n| N/A\n| 16 August 2017\n|<ref name=\"Leon and Kalinga\"/>\n|-\n| 27\n|{{sort|27|DF}}\n!scope=\"row\"| {{flagicon|IND}} [[Prashanth Kalinga]]\n|[[Bengaluru FC Academy]]\n| N/A\n| 16 August 2017\n|<ref name=\"Leon and Kalinga\"/>\n|-\n| 45\n|{{sort|45|GK}}\n!scope=\"row\"| {{flagicon|IND}} [[Gurpreet Singh Sandhu]]\n|{{flagicon|NOR}} [[Stab\u00e6k Fotball|Stab\u00e6k]]\n|undisclosed\n| 17 August 2017\n|<ref name=\"Sandhu\"/>\n|-\n| 7\n|{{sort|7|FW}}\n!scope=\"row\"| {{flagicon|VEN}} [[Miku (footballer)|Miku]]\n| {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Rayo Vallecano]]\n| Free agent\n| 29 August 2017\n|<ref name=\"Miku\"/>\n|-\n| 13\n|{{sort|13|MF}}\n!scope=\"row\"| {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Edu Garc\u00eda]]\n| {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Real Zaragoza]]\n| Free agent\n| 3 September 2017\n|<ref name=\"Edu\"/>\n|-\n| 12\n|{{sort|12|FW}}\n!scope=\"row\"| {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Daniel Lucas Segovia]]\n|{{flagicon|AZE}} [[Neft\u00e7i PFK]]\n| Free agent\n| 15 February 2018\n|<ref name=\"Segovia\"/>\n|-\n| 44\n|{{sort|44|MF}}\n!scope=\"row\"| {{flagicon|ESP}} [[V\u00edctor P\u00e9rez Alonso]]\n|{{flagicon|POL}} [[Wis\u0142a Krak\u00f3w]]\n| Free agent\n| 2 March 2018\n| <ref name=\"Alonso\"/>\n|}\n\n====Out====\n{|class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center; text-align:left\"\n!No.\n!scope=\"col\"|Position\n!scope=\"col\"|Player\n!scope=\"col\"