ant coach Carles Cuadrat steps down|date=29 December 2017|work=Goal.com}}</ref>\n\n:''As of July 2017.''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bengalurufc.com/detailclubnews.php?id=222 |title=Bengaluru FC fortify first team staff |date=9 December 2015 |work=Bengaluru FC |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222163120/http://bengalurufc.com/detailclubnews.php?id=222 |archivedate=22 December 2015 |df=dmy }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.goal.com/en-india/news/1064/i-league/2016/06/13/24587172/i-league-news-bengaluru-fc-appoint-john-kila-as-new-head-of|title=I-League News: Bengaluru FC appoint John Kila as new Head of Youth Development|date=13 June 2016|work=Goal.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bengalurufc.com/naushad-moosa-joins-bengaluru-fc-indian-assistant-coach/ |title=NAUSHAD MOOSA JOINS BENGALURU FC AS INDIAN ASSISTANT COACH |date=29 June 2017 |work=Bengaluru FC}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Position\n! Name\n|-\n| Head Coach\n| {{flagicon|SPA}} [[Albert Roca]]\n|-\n| Assistant Coach\n| {{flagicon|ESP}} Marc Huguet \n|-\n| Assistant Coach (India)\n| {{flagicon|IND}} [[Naushad Moosa]]\n|-\n| Goalkeeping Coach\n| {{flagicon|ESP}} Edu Gasol\n|-\n| Head of Youth Development\n| {{flagicon|NED}} John Killa\n|-\n| Under-18 coach\n| {{flagicon|IND}} John Kenneth Raj\n|-\n| Head physiotherapist\n| {{flagicon|RSA}} Timothy Vadachalam\n|-\n| Head of sports sciences\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} Donavan Pillai\n|}\n{{clear}}\n\n==Player statistics==\n\n===Appearances and goals===\n{{Efs start|[[2017\u201318 Indian Super League season|ISL]]|[[Asian Football Confederation|AFC]]|[[2018 Indian Super Cup|Super Cup]]}}\n|-\n! colspan=12 style=background:#dcdcdc; text-align:center| Goalkeepers\n{{Efs player|no=1|name=[[Gurpreet Singh Sandhu]]|pos=GK|nat=IND|19+0|0|4+0|0|4+0|0}}\n{{Efs player|no=23|name=[[Abhra Mondal]]|pos=GK|nat=IND|0+1|0|0+0|0|0+0|0}}\n{{Efs player|no=28|name=[[Lalthuammawia Ralte]]|pos=GK|nat=IND|2+0|0|10+0|0|0+0|0 }}\n{{Efs player|no=