ign:left\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:130px;\"| Month\n! style=\"width:200px;\"| Player\n! style=\"width:50px;\"| Votes\n|-\n| November\n| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Erik Paartalu]]\n| 57%<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/bengalurufc/status/937653935157870592|title=WINNER! With 57% of all the votes, @ErikPaartalu is your Fan Player of the Month for November. Congratulations, Big E! |publisher=[[Bengaluru FC]] |date=4 December 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| December\n| {{flagicon|VEN}} [[Miku (footballer)|Miku]]\n| 66%<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/bengalurufc/status/948530185376219137|title=With 66% of all the votes, Miku is our @IndiaEpson Fan Player of the Month for December 2017! Here are his numbers from the month gone by. |publisher=[[Bengaluru FC]] |date=3 January 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| January \n| {{flagicon|IND}} [[Sunil Chhetri]]\n| 58%<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/bengalurufc/status/960102463880642560|title=With 58% of all votes, skipper Sunil Chhetri is your BFC Fan Player of the Month for January. |publisher=[[Bengaluru FC]] |date=4 February 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| February  \n| {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Dimas Delgado]]\n| 41%<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/bengalurufc/status/970964100279820288|title=With two Man of the Match performances, Blues' midfielder Dimas Delgado is your Epson Fan Player of the Month for February 2018.  |publisher=[[Bengaluru FC]] |date=6 March 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| March  \n| {{flagicon|IND}} [[Udanta Singh]]\n| 41%<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/bengalurufc/status/982161318797963265|title=WINNER! With 41% of all votes, winger @UdantaK is your @IndiaEpson Fan Player of the Month for March.|publisher=[[Bengaluru FC]] |date=6 April 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| April  \n| {{flagicon|ESP}} [[V\u00edctor P\u00e9rez Alonso]]\n| 33%<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/bengalurufc/status/993402209147568130|title=For his stellar show in the Super Cup, and with 33% of all the votes, Spanish midfielder Victor Perez is your @IndiaEpson Fan Player