ala\n|team2=[[Kerala Blasters FC|Kerala Blasters]]\n|goals1=\n* [[Boithang Haokip|B.Haokip]] {{yel|19}}\n* [[Miku (footballer)|Miku]] {{goal|90+1}}\n* [[Udanta Singh|Udanta]] {{goal|90+3}}\n|goals2= \n|location=[[Bengaluru]]\n|stadium=[[Sree Kanteerava Stadium]]\n|attendance=25,373\n|referee= [[Pranjal Banerjee]]\n|result=W\n|motm =[[Miku (footballer)|Miku]] (Bengaluru FC) \n}}\n\n====Playoffs====\n{{Football box collapsible |id=\"Pune City v Bengaluru FC\"\n|round = Semi-Finals\n|date= 7 March 2018\n|time= 20:00 [[Indian Standard Time|IST]]\n|team1=[[FC Pune City|Pune City]]\n|score=0\u20130\n|report=https://www.indiansuperleague.com/news/pune-bengaluru-play-out-a-goalless-draw-in-the-first-leg\n|team2=Bengaluru FC\n|goals1=\n* [[Gurtej Singh|G. Singh]] {{yel|30}}\n* [[Marko Stankovi\u0107|Stankovi\u0107]] {{yel|87}}\n|goals2=\n* [[Dimas Delgado|Dimas]] {{yel|27}}\n* [[Subhasish Bose|Subashish]] {{yel|71}}\n|location=[[Pune]]\n|stadium=[[Shree Shiv Chhatrapati Sports Complex]]\n|attendance=9,284\n|referee=Om Prakash Thakur\n|result=D\n|motm = [[Marko Stankovi\u0107]] (Pune City)\n}}\n{{Football box collapsible |id=\"Bengaluru FC v Pune City\"\n|round = Semi-Finals\n|date= 11 March 2018\n|time= 20:00 [[Indian Standard Time|IST]]\n|team1=Bengaluru FC\n|score=3\u20131\n|report=http://www.bengalurufc.com/bengaluru-fc-keep-final-date-fortress/\n|team2=[[FC Pune City|Pune City]]\n|goals1=\n* [[Sunil Chhetri|Chhetri]] {{goal|15||65|pen.|89}}\n* [[Subhasish Bose|Subashish]] {{yel|44}}\n|goals2= \n* [[Sahil Panwar|Panwar]] {{yel|31}}\n* [[Diego Carlos|Carlos]] {{yel|34}}\n* [[Rafa (footballer)|Rafa]] {{yel|37}}\n* [[Jonatan Lucca|Lucca]] {{goal|82}}\n|location=[[Bengaluru]]\n|stadium=[[Sree Kanteerava Stadium]]\n|attendance=24,214\n|referee=Turki Al-Khudair\n|result=W\n|motm = [[Sunil Chhetri]] (Bengaluru FC) \n}}\n;Final\n{{Football box collapsible |id=\"Bengaluru FC v Chennaiyin FC\"\n|round = [[2018 Indian Super League Final|Final]]\n|date= 17 March 2018\n|time= 20:00 [[